                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/7481" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">OB-0343</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2243 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">“把朋友搞得多多的”：三叶草组织合伙模式护航海大集团“一带一路”</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Keep Making More Friends: &quot;Shamrock Partnership&quot; Escorting HAID Strategic Business Division to The Belt and Road Initiative</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">刘平青，霍春阳，熊伟，袁云云，张帆，刘东旭，赵洱岽</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">北京理工大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">广东海大集团股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">农林牧副渔业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规划计划部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">13 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">“一带一路”；共同富裕；组织变革；三叶草组织；合伙制；2023百优案例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">The Belt and Road Initiative; Common Prosperity for Everyone; Organizational Change; Shamrock Organization; Partnership</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作为国家重要战略部署，“一带一路”倡议一直以来鲜能获得国内企业有效的积极响应。究其原因，旧模式难调整、合伙人难管理、新市场难扎根等困境，是令这些企业在出海路上“羞羞答答”的根源。本案例描述了立足广州的海大集团战略发展事业部（简称“战发部”）通过对组织变革模式的探索，积极响应国家“一带一路”倡议的历程。在其“比学赶帮超”中，战发部创造性地将合伙制与三叶草组织模式结合，逐步形成了三叶草组织合伙模式。经过“铸船”“破浪”“远航”三个阶段，战发部将企业核心人员、海外合伙人、海外劳动力三者有机结合，有效解决了组织模式“变而不革”、合伙人“合而不伙”、新市场“开而不发”等难题。随着海外市场的成功拓展和合伙模式的不断推广，战发部不仅实现了与当地国家的共赢共富，还通过践行企业社会责任，促进了“一带一路”战略的持续发展，为国内企业“走出去”提供了经验借鉴，为教学贡献了稀缺案例。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">As a crucial national strategy, the Belt and Road Initiative (BRI) has rarely received positive responses from Chinese companies. The main reason for their reluctance is the difficulty of changing business models, managing partnerships, and entering overseas markets. This case illustrates how the HAID Strategic Development Division (HSDD) responded to BRI by innovating its organizational model. Through a process of Comparing-Learning-Chasing-Helping-Exceeding, HSDD creatively integrated the Shamrock Organization and the Partnership into a Shamrock Partnership model. Through the stages of Shipbuilding, Waves-breaking, and Sailing-Away, HSDD effectively combined its core employees with its overseas partners and laborers. This helped HSDD overcome its challenges in organizational transformation, partnership management, and market development. By expanding the Shamrock Partnership and exploring new markets, HSDD contributed to the prosperity of the BRI-related countries. Moreover, by practicing social responsibility, HSDD set a practical example for other Chinese companies and enriched valuable teaching materials for relevant case studies.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《组织行为学》、《管理学》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">组织变革；合伙制；三叶草组织</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023-09</td>
                            </tr>
